<h4><a href="https://hypebeast.cn/2020/12/adidas-originals-all-stan-smith-sustainable-shoes-news">Adidas Originals 宣布未来全数 Stan Smith 鞋款将以可持续性材料制作</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1386618" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/https___hypebeast.com_wp-content_blogs.dir_4_files_2020_12_adidas-originals-all-stan-smith-sustainable-shoes-news-1.jpg" alt="" width="1280" height="853" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/https___hypebeast.com_wp-content_blogs.dir_4_files_2020_12_adidas-originals-all-stan-smith-sustainable-shoes-news-1.jpg 1280w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/https___hypebeast.com_wp-content_blogs.dir_4_files_2020_12_adidas-originals-all-stan-smith-sustainable-shoes-news-1-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/https___hypebeast.com_wp-content_blogs.dir_4_files_2020_12_adidas-originals-all-stan-smith-sustainable-shoes-news-1-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/https___hypebeast.com_wp-content_blogs.dir_4_files_2020_12_adidas-originals-all-stan-smith-sustainable-shoes-news-1-1024x682.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1280px) 100vw, 1280px" /></p>
<p>据 Hypebeast 报道，被吉尼斯世界纪录认定为世界上最畅销运动鞋履 Adidas Originals 的 Stan Smith 计划将所有原料改为可持续性材料，到 2024 年所有原料皆从纯聚酯转变成再生聚酯。而为了庆祝 Stan Smith 在 2021 年的 50 岁生日，Adidas 也将带来全新材质款式，以再生橡胶作为外底，鞋带利用再生材料制成，努力实现可持续的发展目标。</p>
<h4><a href="https://new.qq.com/omn/20201215/20201215A0DHFJ00.html">财政部原副部长朱光耀：是时候对数字税收进行总体研究了</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1386621" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/US04dXUrQo0QQLUwrOUv8BHoqTk.jpg" alt="" width="2560" height="1707" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/US04dXUrQo0QQLUwrOUv8BHoqTk.jpg 2560w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/US04dXUrQo0QQLUwrOUv8BHoqTk-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/US04dXUrQo0QQLUwrOUv8BHoqTk-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/US04dXUrQo0QQLUwrOUv8BHoqTk-1024x683.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px" /></p>
<p>据腾讯一线报道，财政部原副部长朱光耀日前表示，是时候对数字税收进行总体研究，特别是对拥有大型科技平台、拥有大型数据平台、拥有巨大消费者流量的平台，进行针对性研究需要提上日程。「就像银行可能大而不能倒一样，巨型数字平台也可能有大而不能拆的特征。如何进行合理的监管，对世界都提出了挑战。」</p>
