<h4><a href="https://hmgroup.com/media/news/general-news-2020/new-business-venture-singular-society-explores-membership-based-.html">H&amp;M 集团推首个会员制品牌 Singular Society</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1386615" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/HM-Singular-Society-004-768x512.jpg" alt="" width="768" height="512" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/HM-Singular-Society-004-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/HM-Singular-Society-004-768x512-360x240.jpg 360w" sizes="(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px" /></p>
<p>以快时尚闻名的瑞典时尚集团 H&amp;M 推出首个会员制品牌 Singular Society。该品牌以订阅模式为基础，向会员提供高品质的服饰家居及必备日用品。物美价廉是 Singular Society 诞生的核心。根据品牌网站公告，Singular Society 将以成本价出售所有这些高质量和设计的产品。</p>
<p>目前品牌网站上罗列的 105 件商品涵盖了男装女装、家居用具、厨房用品等方方面面。</p>
<h4><a href="https://tech.ifeng.com/c/82Dr2c3wOJt">央行：不得排斥和歧视现金支付，鼓励支付方式和谐发展</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-845381" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/rmb.jpg" alt="" width="1200" height="750" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/rmb.jpg 1200w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/rmb-360x225.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/rmb-768x480.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/rmb-1024x640.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" /></p>
<p>央行就规范人民币现金收付行为有关事项公告称，人民币是我国的法定货币，人民币现金是我国境内最基础的支付手段，任何单位和个人不得拒收。公告称，消费及支付方式创新要坚持有利于畅通支付流通环境、有利于保障民生、有利于提升公众的幸福感和获得感，不得采取歧视性或非便利性措施排斥现金支付，造成「数字鸿沟」。</p>
<h3><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1293890" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/wangyo.png" alt="" width="1029" height="180" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/wangyo.png 1029w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/wangyo-360x63.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/wangyo-768x134.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/wangyo-1024x179.png 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1029px) 100vw, 1029px" /></h3>
<h4><a href="https://s.weibo.com/weibo?q=%23%E7%BB%93%E5%A9%9A%E6%9C%89%E5%BF%85%E8%A6%81%E4%B9%B0%E6%88%BF%E5%90%97%23">结婚有必要买房吗？</a></h4>
<p>韩国统计厅近日发布一项统计资料显示，韩国无住房新婚家庭占比近 6 成。韩国不以买房子为终极目标，所以有房子的年轻人很少，租房子的很多。但中国很多人结婚，依然会优先考虑房子的问题，保证自己有一个稳定的住所。</p>
<p>网友：「没必要结婚。」「有钱为什么要考虑买不买，没钱还考虑什么买不买。」​「没房子结什么婚？俩人居无定所，生个崽子居无定所，没有房崽子怎么上学怎么读书！」</p>
<h3><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1357581" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/wed-1.png" alt="" width="1029" height="153" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/wed-1.png 1029w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/wed-1-360x54.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/wed-1-768x114.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/wed-1-1024x152.png 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1029px) 100vw, 1029px" /></h3>
